埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 分享他给查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的应对名声的建议https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-shares-advice-he-gave-to-chappell-roan-on-coping-with-fame-3826631?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=elton-约翰向查佩尔·罗恩分享了他应对名声的建议Surej SinghTue, 07 Jan 2025 07:49:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3826631 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>去年，在罗恩 (Roan) 迅速崛起后，她和约翰 (John) 在 FaceTime 上进行了多次聊天</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-shares-advice-he-gave-to-chappell-roan-on-coping-with-fame-3826631">埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 分享了他向查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 提供的应对名气的建议，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/elton-john-chappell-roan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John)</a>透露了他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a>分享的关于应对名气的建议 - 看看下面必须传授的智慧。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="391" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-chapell-roan-interview-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-3582467"><b>Chappell Roan：流行超新星，感觉就像“变装皇后”女孩之一</b></a></li></ul><p>2024 年，查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的名气飞速上升，这在很大程度上要归功于她 2023 年的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">中西部公主的兴衰》(The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess</a> )。例如， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roans-lollapalooza-set-is-among-the-festivals-most-attended-in-history-3781184">她的 Lollapalooza 演出是该音乐节历史上参加人数最多的演出之一</a>。在这一年的其他地方，她开启了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗迪戈 (Olivia Rodigo)</a>的“Guts”巡演，然后在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉 (Coachella) 音乐节</a>和州长舞会上上演了成为头条新闻的表演。</p><p>然而，对于这位歌手来说，这并不是一次完全积极的经历，她也目睹了自己突然成名所带来的压力。罗恩在过去几个月里直言不讳地讲述了她的成名经历，发泄了极端粉丝行为的常态化，包括“跟踪、在网上说废话、[那些人]不会让你孤单[和]在家里对你大喊大叫。”民众”。 </p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><div id="taboola-mid-article" class="trc_related_container tbl-feed-container render-late-effect tbl-feed-frame-DIVIDER" data-feed-container-num="1" data-feed-main-container-id="taboola-mid-article" data-parent-placement-name="Mid Article" data-pub-lang="en"><div class="tbl-feed-header tbl-logo-none-position"><figure id="attachment_3824876" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3824876" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3824876" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing.jpg" alt="查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 10 月 25 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 NYA EAST 举行的 Netflix 奥利维亚·罗德里戈：GUTS 世界巡演首映式。 （弗雷泽·哈里森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Chappell-Roan-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3824876" class="wp-caption-text">查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 出席 2024 年 10 月 25 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 NYA EAST 举行的 Netflix 奥利维亚·罗德里戈：GUTS 世界巡演首映式。 （弗雷泽·哈里森/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467"><i>《NME》封面</i>明星</a>还将名气比作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">“有虐待倾向的前夫”</a> 。在其他地方，她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tiktok">TikTok</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">分享了她对“奇怪”和“令人毛骨悚然”的粉丝的看法</a>，并指出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-writes-to-superfans-about-predatory-behaviour-women-dont-owe-you-shit-3786492">所谓“超级粉丝”的“掠夺性行为”</a> ，其中包括“未经同意的身体和社交互动”。</p></div></div></div><p>自从进入名气的上层以来，Chappell Roan 一直向<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramores-hayley-williams-supports-chappell-roans-brave-and-unfortunately-necessary-boundary-comments-3787404">Paramore 的 Hayley Williams</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-was-the-first-person-to-reach-out-to-chappell-roan-about-pressures-of-fame-this-is-about-to-get-really-hard-3795321">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-lorde-sent-her-a-list-of-ways-to-cope-with-negativity-and-fame-3794353">Lorde</a>等人寻求建议。埃尔顿·约翰（Elton John）是一位为她提供智慧之言的偶像，她曾多次与他进行 FaceTime 通话。</p><p>去年 12 月，埃尔顿在接受<a href="https://theankler.com/p/elton-john-brandi-carlile-never-too-late-billie-eilish-chappell-roan" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>The Ankler</em></a>采访时透露了他在聊天中与她分享的一些关于管理名誉的建议：“查佩尔对她突然的成功有点不知所措——尽管她已经写作很长时间了，但这真的很友善。”膨胀得非常快。我只是试着让她平静下来，然后说：‘听着，没关系。没关系。做你想做的事。不要听任何人的。按照自己的速度行走。不要听唱片公司说：“我们想要另一张专辑，我们想要另一张专辑。”当你准备好时就去做。” </p><figure id="attachment_3821171" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3821171" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3821171" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name.jpg" alt="艾尔顿约翰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/EltonJohn-changed-name-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3821171" class="wp-caption-text">艾尔顿约翰。图片来源：戴夫·贝内特/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“我有这样的经验。我经历过生命中的一切，知道在音乐中该做什么，看到人们来，看到人们离开。有时它们消失得太快了。”</p><p>此外，他还向自己传达了自己的长寿之道，并分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>等艺术家迅速取得成功的其他实例：其中一个人已经 77 岁了。我可能还像年轻时一样受欢迎，这真是一个奇迹。但很高兴能够将这些东西传递下去并在人们身上看到结果。有一位英国歌手 RAYE，他是一位出色的艺术家。她原则上离开了唱片公司，做了自己想做的事。它完全成功了。我非常钦佩她这样做。她表明了自己的立场，而她的结果就是她自己对自己应该做什么的看法。它刚刚爆炸了。”</p><p> “比莉·艾利什是另一位。我记得看到她的第一张专辑每周都爬上<em>公告</em>牌排行榜：口碑，口碑，口碑，突然间，她就成为了我能想到的最伟大的女艺术家之一。我的意思是，这张新专辑非常出色，你可以说她的所有专辑都是如此。每一个都是不同的，每一个都是一个进步。那有多棒？我从中获得了很多能量。” </p><figure id="attachment_3797166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3797166" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3797166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/chappell-roan@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3797166" class="wp-caption-text">查普尔·罗恩.图片来源：吉姆·戴森/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>Elton John 一直是 Roan 的长期粉丝，并于 2024 年 8 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-congratulates-chappell-roan-on-chart-success-the-meteoric-rise-of-a-midwestern-princess-3782611">祝贺“HOT TO GO!”</a>歌手在该月发行近一年后凭借《 <a style="font-f